    <item>
      <title>Altman 寻求为人工智能芯片工厂网络筹集数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/altman-seeks-to-raise-billions-for-network-of-ai-chip-factories</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据几位知情人士透露，OpenAI 首席执行官萨姆·奥尔特曼 (Sam Altman) 一直致力于从全球投资者那里筹集数十亿美元资金用于一家芯片企业，他的目标是利用这些资金建立一个工厂网络来制造半导体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/altman-seeks-to-raise-billions-for-network-of-ai-chip-factories</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 17:10:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Centerview 创始人表示，人工智能意味着孩子们应该学习良好的判断力，而不是代码</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/ai-means-kids-should-learn-good-judgment-not-code-says-centerview-ceo-effron</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约一位顶级银行家表示，人工智能的发展意味着年轻人应该学习如何批判性思考并拥有良好的判断力，而不是培养编码技能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/ai-means-kids-should-learn-good-judgment-not-code-says-centerview-ceo-effron</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 16:52:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标普因再融资风险将 Atos 评级进一步下调为垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/s-p-downgrades-atos-deeper-into-junk-on-asset-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级将 Atos SE 的评级下调至垃圾级，称这家法国软件公司的信用指标疲软，关键资产出售面临风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/s-p-downgrades-atos-deeper-into-junk-on-asset-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 16:21:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦拨款 4 亿美元用于北极无人机监视</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/denmark-allocates-400-million-to-arctic-drone-surveillance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦将在未来十年花费 27 亿克朗（4 亿美元）购买远程无人机，以帮助监测北极和北大西洋，并确保丹麦在格陵兰岛和法罗群岛的主权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/denmark-allocates-400-million-to-arctic-drone-surveillance</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 16:12:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AMD 创历史新高表明人工智能驱动的芯片拉力赛又一档</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/amd-s-record-high-shows-ai-fueled-chip-rally-has-another-gear</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着围绕半导体行业增长前景的乐观情绪重新抬头，Advanced Micro Devices Inc. 有望创下 11 月份以来表现最好的一周，甚至超过了人工智能宠儿 Nvidia Corp.。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/amd-s-record-high-shows-ai-fueled-chip-rally-has-another-gear</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 15:40:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
